org.apache.zeppelin.interpreter.remote

Class RemoteInterpreterEventClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.zeppelin.interpreter.remote.RemoteInterpreterEventClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AngularObjectRegistryListener, ResourcePoolConnector

    public class RemoteInterpreterEventClient
extends Object
implements ResourcePoolConnector, AngularObjectRegistryListener
    This class is used to communicate with ZeppelinServer via thrift. All the methods are synchronized because thrift client is not thread safe.
